text: Gayane Chiloyan (, born 27 September 2000 in YerevanGayane Chiloyan at sport- reference.com) is an Armenian sprinter. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 200 metres race; her time of 25.03 seconds in the heats did not qualify her for the semifinals. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Armenian female sprinters Category:Olympic athletes of Armenia Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics
